de.jpdigital.maven.plugins.hibernate4ddl

Enum Dialect

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Dialect>
      • de.jpdigital.maven.plugins.hibernate4ddl.Dialect
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Dialect>

    public enum Dialect
extends Enum<Dialect>
    This enumeration provides constants for all dialects supported by Hibernate. The dialects supported by Hibernate can be found in the Hibernate documentation. Also this enumeration provides the convenient method getDialectClass() for getting the class name of the Hibernate dialect.
    Author:
    Jens Pelzetter
